## 7. Regra especial

<span style="color:#e74c3c"><strong>Exceção: HAVE → HAS</strong></span>

O verbo **to have** é irregular na 3ª pessoa do singular.

### Exemplo: TO HAVE (ter)

* I have
* You have
* <span style="color:#c0392b"><strong>He has</strong></span>
* <span style="color:#c0392b"><strong>She has</strong></span>
* <span style="color:#c0392b"><strong>It has</strong></span>
* We have
* You have
* They have

---

## 8. Resumo geral

* Apenas <span style="color:#c0392b"><strong>He / She / It</strong></span> conjugam o verbo
* O, S, X, SH, CH → + ES
* Vogal + Y → + S
* Consoante + Y → IES
* Restante → + S
* Have → Has
